<div class="story">
<p>Port Trinitie is an ocean to sound community in Duck with an active home owners association and an HOA fee. The HOA takes care of the private road, the ocean side community pool, sound front community pool w/ pier and gazebo on the end of the pier, 2 tennis courts  and ocean accesses. The community is a mixture of single family homes and timeshare units. To the north is the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/sea-tern.asp" title="Sea Tern">Sea Tern</a> and to the south is the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/wild-duck-dunes.asp" title="Wild Duck Dunes">Wild Duck Dunes</a>. </p>
